Ebbro 43771 Toyota Supra (JZA80) 2005 JGTC Series GT500 Class Winner T. Takagi/Y. Tachikawa

Purchased: 2014
Manufacturer page: http://www.ebbro.jp/SHOP/43771.html

Toranosuke Takagi & Yuji Tachikawa raced for ZENT Toyota Team Cerumo in the 2005 JGTC Series. In addition to 3 wins they took the title in the GT500 class. This would be the 4th and final time a Supra won the JGTC series making it the 2nd most successful car in the JGTC series behind the Nissan Skyline GT-R.
